  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Crash Test Oliver offers you a sweet 2,5D platformer experience with loads of jump'n'run, different types of enemies, puzzles and big boss fights. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.poster.avif?t=1734967201\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.webm?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.mp4?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>You are a Crash Test Dummy No. 2.409, codename \"Oliver\". Scientists are sending thousands of dummies like you into a simulation to test a baseball cap full of brand new features. None of the other test subjects have passed the simulation so far. Will you finally make a difference?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cap features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Punch<br></li><li>Stomp<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>Walljump<br></li><li>Swim</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.poster.avif?t=1734967201\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.webm?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.mp4?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>Crash Test Oliver offers you a sweet 2,5D platformer experience with loads of jump'n'run, different types of enemies, puzzles and big boss fights. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.poster.avif?t=1734967201\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.webm?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/35547ef0fc762183477e93dc80308103.mp4?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>You are a Crash Test Dummy No. 2.409, codename \"Oliver\". Scientists are sending thousands of dummies like you into a simulation to test a baseball cap full of brand new features. None of the other test subjects have passed the simulation so far. Will you finally make a difference?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cap features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Punch<br></li><li>Stomp<br></li><li>Dash<br></li><li>Walljump<br></li><li>Swim</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.poster.avif?t=1734967201\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.webm?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1936860/extras/928e172bc2049e272056aaa81df72530.mp4?t=1734967201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
